七座建筑和一个庭院组成，里面住满了来自加沙地带的基督徒家庭。空袭发生在晚上 7 点 30 分左右，当时正在分发晚餐。「我们将重建被损毁的地方。但那些被杀害的人，我们无法让他们复活。」43 岁的教堂志愿者易卜拉欣·贾尚（Ibrahim Jahshan）在电话里说道。 10 月 20 日，加沙城，当地一座东正教教堂遭以军空袭，建筑倒塌满地废墟。图自 IC Photo 东正教教堂也被以色列炸了，至少 18 人死亡"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6a6bd794b83586ef193ceb2c8dedd15b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "97 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627148736"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIkY3hmNKpza0SEAMaCTEwMTY0NTI2NyC/0M2pBjAAON4CQAZyCTYyNzE0ODczNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1697886361.722131", "card_id": "Q_626979503", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "电影《河边的错误》中有哪些值得回味的细节？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a345555099eb04da1bd5e096329a0453_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626979503"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkY3hmNKpza0SEAMaCTEwMTYwNzgwNSD568epBjAAOBBAB3IJNjI2OTc5NTAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1697886361.722675", "card_id": "Q_538560106", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "INTP 是怎么看待 INFP 的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area"